      • doSSHAction

        private java.lang.String doSSHAction(com.jcraft.jsch.ChannelSftp channel,
                                     java.lang.String src,
                                     java.lang.String dst,
                                     int uid,
                                     int gid,
                                     int permiss,
                                     org.apache.jmeter.samplers.SampleResult res)
                              throws com.jcraft.jsch.SftpException,
                                     java.io.IOException,
                                     java.lang.Exception
        Executes a the given command inside a short-lived channel in the session. Performance could be likely improved by reusing a single channel, though the gains would be minimal compared to sharing the Session.
        Parameters:
        channel - channel on which the sftp command is sent
        scr - source file on which the command is executed
        dst - destination file on which the command is executed
        uid - numeric user id for the chown command
        gid - numeric group id for the chgrp command
        permiss - numeric permissions for the chmod command
        res - contains the result of the operation
        Returns:
        All standard output from the command
        Throws:
        com.jcraft.jsch.JSchException
        com.jcraft.jsch.SftpException
        java.io.IOException
        java.lang.Exception
